  "purpose": "A funded award from a foundation, government agency, or corporate funder, with specific use restrictions, reporting requirements, and a defined performance period. Distinct from individual Donations because Grants involve formal applications, restricted use of funds, and multi-stage workflows (proposal, review, award, payment, reporting, closeout).",
